org.cef.network

类 CefRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefRequest

  • public abstract class CefRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent a web request. The methods of this class may be called on any thread. (用于表示Web请求的类。此类的方法可以在任何线程上调用。)

      • getIdentifier

        public abstract long getIdentifier()
        Returns the globally unique identifier for this request or 0 if not specified. Can be used by CefRequestHandler implementations in the browser process to track a single request across multiple callbacks. (返回此请求的全局唯一标识符；如果未指定，则返回0。可以由CefRequestHandler实现在浏览器进程中使用，以跨多个回调跟踪单个请求。)

      • getMethod

        public abstract java.lang.String getMethod()
        Get the request method type. The value will default to POST if post data is provided and GET otherwise. (获取请求方法类型。如果提供了发布数据，则该值默认为POST，否则为GET。)

      • getPostData

      • getResourceType

        public abstract CefRequest.ResourceType getResourceType()
        Get the resource type for this request. Accurate resource type information may only be available in the browser process. (获取此请求的资源类型。准确的资源类型信息可能仅在浏览器过程中可用。)

      • getTransitionType

        public abstract CefRequest.TransitionType getTransitionType()
        Get the transition type for this request. Only available in the browser process and only applies to requests that represent a main frame or sub-frame navigation. (获取此请求的转换类型。仅在浏览器过程中可用，并且仅适用于代表主框架或子框架导航的请求。)

        public abstract void setReferrer(java.lang.String url,
                                 CefRequest.ReferrerPolicy policy)
        Set the referrer URL and policy. If non-empty the referrer URL must be fully qualified with an HTTP or HTTPS scheme component. Any username, password or ref component will be removed. (设置引荐来源网址和策略。如果非空，则引用网址必须使用HTTP或HTTPS方案组件进行完全限定。任何用户名，密码或参考组件将被删除。)
